==English==

===Etymology===
From {{ON.}} [[Eirikr]] "honoured ruler", "complete ruler", or "kingly, ever so powerful".

===Proper noun===
'''Eric'''

# A male [[given name]] of Germanic origins.  Entered the English language via the Irish.

Also known as a tall oaf who just so happens to be the gayest kid in the world and who thinks he is black.